79-kaltura-non-gaap-eps-of-001-beats-by-003-revenue-of-443m-beats-by-124m\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4255279-kaltura-non-gaap-eps-of-001-beats-by-003-revenue-of-443m-beats-by-124m\" target=\"_blank\">financial results</a> in early November, beating both revenue and earnings estimates followed by the stock rising sharply as a result.</p> <p>I previously wrote about KLTR in August 2023 with a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4622713-kaltura-scant-revenue-growth-2023\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4622713-kaltura-scant-revenue-growth-2023\" target=\"_blank\">Hold</a> outlook due</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745685-kaltura-improves-operating-efficiencies-but-revenue-growth-lags", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:24:14", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745683", "title": "Micron Technology Q1: Undervalued And Innovative", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Micron Technology Inc. One of american leader in semiconductor devices, dynamic random-access memory, flash memory, USB flash drives, solid-state drives.\" data-id=\"1150565928\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5760px\" height=\"3840px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">vzphotos</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis </h2> <p><b>Micron Technology, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) reported a solid <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387691-micron-tumbles-weak-q2-forecast-fails-to-overcome-q1-results\">Q1 2025</a>, with revenue and profits hitting record levels in the three months ended November 2024. However, disappointing <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387865-earnings-snapshot-micron-fq2-outlook-undershoots-expectations-while-fq1-tops-consensus\">Q2 2024 guidance</a> weighed down on shares. Two</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745683-micron-technology-q1-undervalued-and-innovative", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:19:38", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745681", "title": "HIGH: When Options Spreads Do Not Work", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2058537479/image_2058537479.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Only 1 of 5 ladders reach in ascending order\