s://seekingalpha.com/article/4745675-patterson-uti-cheap-despite-leading-yield-and-buyback-and-power-segment-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 23:37:01", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745674", "title": "Paychex: Payrolling In Profits, But Valuation Could Use A Check", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tablet, computer and business woman with online management, HR administration software and planning. Digital technology, laptop and human resources person scroll, search or payroll on company website\" data-id=\"1542683788\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1542683788/image_1542683788.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DMP/E+ via Getty Images